POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (49): GLOBAL (WILD POLIOVIRUS TYPE 1, CIRCULATING VACCINE-DERIVED POLIOVIRUS), PAKISTAN (NON-PARALYTIC VIRUS SHEDDERS), REQUEST FOR INFORMATION
